version_description: There weren't any versions of the Beach Boys interpretation of this song.

song_name: Dont Talk Put Your Head On My Shoulder

version_description: From the Beach Boys' unreleased 1977 Adult/Child album.
This version captures the jazz-style chords of Carl Wilson, on a 12 string. With the Capo on 2, using open chords, wherever possible.
Verse chords are ascending/descending. Slash chords will make a big difference.
Subtler chords in Verse 1 and 2, fuller arrangement, includes some backing vocals, chord legend included,.
